{"tid":2361760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛系默站式港鐵趕工","createTime":"2021-01-11T03:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T18:22:11.000Z","uid":105567,"like":299,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2861a16785571fe1dbbf06db0453c939187e46","tid":2361760,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"【佛系默站式港鐵趕工】<br />\n<br />\n不得不贊美港鐵的勇氣﹐和不變的堅毅。<br />\n<br />\n大概是一個宣傳﹐港鐵將一個bifurcation works﹐即鋪設分叉路軌和相關訊號系統工程﹐說成史上最複雜﹐所以要每周或隔周星期日封旺角東至紅磡站工作。<br />\n<br />\nFine﹐港鐵有噏得出口的勇氣和出醜的堅毅。相信是港鐵自己流出來的相片﹐哀哉﹐今日開始鋪設分叉路軌﹐30多人在「趕工」﹐但無一個在工作。還有香港仿佛好像北韓般﹐做工程是赤手空拳﹐30多人無人拿著工具、連他們身邊都無。而更重要的﹐要鋪設的路軌都無❗<br />\n<br />\n怪不得﹐港鐵工程總要延誤﹐或花這麼多錢❗港鐵管理層那股當香港人傻的勇氣﹐真係經典❗<br />\n<br />\n#旺角至紅磡站封站趕工<br />\n#佛系默站式港鐵趕工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dmu4KGk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmu4KGk.jpg&h=3106961c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19316ecb4a8096d012530d3539c292c48f413469","tid":2361760,"uid":110952,"like":21,"dislike":108,"score":-87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed1c5b99c5d5bd1724ffe69913886ffc368f6d7","tid":2361760,"uid":60434,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"等緊料開工啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5251bd411b98154d49f75dfe67ef93df631c6a59","tid":2361760,"uid":53062,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:17:35.000Z","msg":"香港工程特色，一個人做野，四個人睇住人做野，"},{"pid":"135dbd8601c26d43367cb0c151d92d18210de0c5","tid":2361760,"uid":370061,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"quote":{"pid":"5251bd411b98154d49f75dfe67ef93df631c6a59","tid":2361760,"uid":53062,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:17:35.000Z","msg":"香港工程特色，一個人做野，四個人睇住人做野，"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"cpu0：<img src=\"/assets/faces/